ti theloume?

1. na kanoume queries:
    - severity of issue
    - date range of the issue
    - engine specific
    - all engines

2. na trexei san cronjob pou tha apothikeyei kathe mera ta nea dedomena

3. na xrhsimopoiei mia mongodb vash:
    - retrieve
    - store new
    - by engine

4. na einai extendable, dhladh na mporoume na prosthetoume filtra

5. command line tool: scrap {update,get} <engine> <filter1> <filter2> <filter3> ... <filterN>
